  "description": "<i>Castlevania: Spectral Interlude</i> is a fan made classic 2D action platformer with RPG elements.<br><br>The game started out as a remake of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/nes/castlevania-ii-simons-quest\">Castlevania II: Simon's Quest</a> but took on its own life during development. At the start you are given a magic artifact that can preserve the souls of monsters. You have to visit several points of power near town to summon monsters to kill and collect their energy into the receptacle. The ultimate goal is to summon and kill Dracula himself.",
